{"tid":2340663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★公屋呎價再破萬元！屯門良景邨呎價逾1.3萬 上車客：\"供平過租\"","createTime":"2020-12-25T16:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T09:21:55.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e47013b2fd652ddc0f4de1cb24fbfd9703bbd619","tid":2340663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"屯門公屋呎價重上萬元關口。祥益胡志偉稱，良景邨良偉樓高層6室，實用面積150方呎，上周於已補價自由市場開價235萬港元放盤。上車客在供平過租下，決定入市，平安夜當日睇樓，今日聖誕節簽約，獲減35萬元，以200萬元買樓過節，呎價13,333元。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提，雖然是次屯門公屋呎價再破萬元，但與去年同屋邨同類單位最高呎價逾1.43萬元相比，呎價低近7%。<br />\n<br />\nttps://<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201225/bkn-20201225175550506-1225_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201225%2Fbkn-20201225175550506-1225_00842_001.html&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=c31407b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201225/bkn-20201225175550506-1225_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"942607df657ada4641b6a668bccfcca5001222ca","tid":2340663,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:22:28.000Z","msg":"公屋又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536506e1a83ffe0ff469609a57511b305bc023ec","tid":2340663,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T16:23:04.000Z","msg":"面積150方呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb66c61540137035ea2698471841fffc9ecd8e2","tid":2340663,"uid":4574,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"cit